{"tid":771261,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇卓韻芝早日日大大聲話自己去倫敦讀藝術，但原來畢唔到業？","createTime":"2018-08-07T21:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-08T12:21:46.000Z","uid":50275,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88ff8925b76ee9630b4373e89f015e751ae8837b","tid":771261,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T21:00:51.000Z","msg":"見到有人話佢自稱大藝術家，「倫敦修讀藝術」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來畢唔到業都可以周街唱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係才女#good2# #good2# <br />\n<br />\n「卓韻芝，跨媒體創作人，同時熱愛藝術和旅行。曾到倫敦修讀藝術，並且將經歷用文字輯錄成兩本遊記。最近著作《旅行之必要》反思旅行的意義。旅行與藝術的體驗其實可以互相印證。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/07/zZ6B4T.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2FzZ6B4T.png&h=86908ead&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/08/07/O1jbRI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F08%2F07%2FO1jbRI.png&h=30388870&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"46001e6fd650a55cae9a6af7a05ce8f35e12d48e","tid":771261,"uid":188081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T21:08:04.000Z","msg":"FINE ART 係咪畫功加美術史"},{"pid":"bc8cb9ff05790e7ee027a9f71372553bc107a95d","tid":771261,"uid":66433,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T21:10:07.000Z","msg":"其實有咩人會特登留意佢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"378b6470cdf2187d98f1310493d1c113039c4400","tid":771261,"uid":123308,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bc8cb9ff05790e7ee027a9f71372553bc107a95d","tid":771261,"uid":66433,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":